{
  "stem": "24615.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was bad, because it was no bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was-- you had to stay in line for bread and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then when you got to the-- sometime there was no bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- was real, real bad for us, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, then I was old already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I used to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] work a little, go with a horse and wagon.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I wish to work for people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And used to go to Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, we used to load flour and bring it to other cities and everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and my mother, still she used to trade, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after the-- the Russians, they got-- I had a cousin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a blacksmith, and he came to work in our shop.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I worked with him, I remember I couldn't lift a hammer yet, you know, to-- And-- but the Russians owned it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, they didn't own it, but we worked for them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't work for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So every-- every two weeks, you know, they used-- they used to bring some, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We used to get paid so much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my cousin used to get-- used to get paid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In this way, you'd survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Russians, they were all right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, you couldn't go from one city to another without-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you had to have a-- like a passport, you know, like, a document.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What are you doing in this city, whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, you couldn't go from one-- Even-- even when you used to work, a lot of time, they used to stop you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where are you going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What are you doing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never got into trouble with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
